@startuml readme-oss-module-overview
'==============================================================================
' Diagram  : OSS Module Overview (README companion)
' Version  : v3
' Date     : 2026-06-17
' Audience : README / docs readers — a grouped architecture orientation.
' Type     : SIMPLIFIED MAINTAINED COMPANION of oss-module-dependency.puml.
'            One idea: how the OSS modules layer by responsibility (each module
'            points to what it depends on / the SPI it plugs into).
' Source   : root reactor pom.xml + module-info.java (live source) +
'            oss-module-dependency.puml.
'==============================================================================
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam nodesep 28
skinparam ranksep 34
hide empty members
top to bottom direction

[Spring Boot Starter] as starter
[Bootstrap] as bootstrap
[Runtime] as runtime
[Config Loader] as config
[Core] as core
[LLM API] as llm
[Tools / MCP] as tools
[Providers] as providers

starter   --> bootstrap
bootstrap --> runtime
runtime   --> config
config    --> core
runtime   --> core
runtime   --> llm
tools     ..> core : tool SPI
providers ..> llm  : LLM SPI

' Layout-only ranking: keep the SPI implementors directly below their SPI.
core -[hidden]-> tools
llm  -[hidden]-> providers

@enduml
